{"tid":2261830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立場： 土瓜灣樂民新村 H 座樂智樓有本地確診個案","createTime":"2020-10-28T15:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T15:28:09.000Z","uid":22556,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a7e092507aab31a8aae298cbd891243b33cc8eaf","tid":2261830,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T15:14:37.000Z","msg":"本港連續三日無錄得本地武漢肺炎確診個案，惟有機會再度「斷纜」。九龍城區議會區議員李軒朗在 Facebook 引述消息指，土瓜灣樂民新村 H 座樂智樓有確診個案，屋邨辦亦已安排人手進行全幢消毒清潔。樂民社區主任 Daisy Kwok 亦在其 Facebook 指，確診者的同住家人亦已確診。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3595727223846205/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3595727223846205%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7OBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=9e959574\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3595727223846205/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"a6ae00e10bf334ae685afd3813d35454f9d336f9","tid":2261830,"uid":56714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T15:23:44.000Z","msg":"冇人理啦"},{"pid":"9f132c66b0009c96076183c844030e02dfaf323d","tid":2261830,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T15:28:09.000Z","msg":"垃圾武肺爆唔起第四波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}